title: 04/04/22 DPS Hour 2 - Tiger Woods, Jalen Rose

description:
Hour 2 of the Dan Patrick Show, the guys also speak on Tiger Woods chances on playing in the upcoming Masters tournament. Jalen Rose then joins the show to recap the Final Four, his collegiate career and NBA.
